  "name": "Morrison COU1 CPB hemolysis — validation package (synthetic W-AR-05/D3)",
  "description": "Synthetic credibility package for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump CFD hemolysis model under the CPB Context of Use (Class II, MRL 2). Validation leverages prior in vitro hemolysis experiments on the same pump geometry. The comparator dataset is well-characterized and widely cited, but its experimental blood working fluid differs from the declared CPB COU in a parameter that is mechanistically relevant to hemolysis (hematocrit and temperature regime). The validation narrative treats the comparator as broadly applicable without examining this mismatch, and one validation result is emitted without a formal comparedAgainst link.",
